00:04:15.121 --> 00:04:16.055 line:95%,end
<i>You did your solo.</i>

00:04:16.122 --> 00:04:17.824 line:95%,end
<i>You got a standing ovation.</i>

00:04:17.890 --> 00:04:19.826 line:95%,end
HOLLY: <i>Being at the top</i>
<i>of the pyramid for Nia</i>

00:04:19.892 --> 00:04:21.494 line:95%,end
