00:05:31.264 --> 00:05:33.700 line:5%,start
<i>This week's group number</i>
<i>is called "Taken."</i>

00:05:33.766 --> 00:05:36.369 line:5%,start
<i>And it has to do with four little girls</i>

00:05:36.436 --> 00:05:37.970 line:95%,end
<i>who are all dressed the same,</i>

00:05:38.037 --> 00:05:40.840 line:95%,end
<i>and they're watching this</i>
<i>other little girl.</i>

00:05:40.907 --> 00:05:43.109 line:95%,end
<i>She's dressed in her own color.</i>

00:05:43.176 --> 00:05:44.143 line:95%,end
<i>She's happy.</i>

00:05:44.210 --> 00:05:46.779 line:95%,end
And, of course, they want to be like her.

00:05:46.846 --> 00:05:49.816 line:95%,end
But they know that
that is not a possibility.

00:05:49.882 --> 00:05:51.918 line:95%,end
