00:06:23.282 --> 00:06:26.052 line:95%,end
<i>I don't want my daughter or myself</i>
<i>to step on anybody's toes.</i>

00:06:26.119 --> 00:06:28.654 line:95%,end
<i>But Kendall deserves</i>
<i>to be a part of this team.</i>

00:06:28.721 --> 00:06:30.890 line:5%,start
