00:06:30.957 --> 00:06:33.526 line:5%,start
Here we are.
These moms need to deal with it.

00:06:33.593 --> 00:06:35.695 line:95%,end
You are one lucky little girl.

00:06:35.762 --> 00:06:38.898 line:95%,end
