with these people who have won week

00:06:38.965 --> 00:06:40.266 line:95%,end
after week after week.

00:06:40.333 --> 00:06:43.836 line:95%,end
Every one of those bad habits
that you came to my studio with

00:06:43.903 --> 00:06:46.439 line:95%,end
got worse when you went to Cathy's.

00:06:46.506 --> 00:06:48.875 line:95%,end
Now I have to clean up the mess.
Thank you.

00:06:49.809 --> 00:06:52.445 line:95%,end
Even though I'm letting Kendall
do the group number

00:06:52.512 --> 00:06:55.615 line:95%,end
and I've selected her
for a duet with Mackenzie,

00:06:55.681 --> 00:06:59.619 line:95%,end
she is under no circumstances
a member of the team.

00:06:59.685 --> 00:07:02.655 line:95%,end
She is still a guest at the
Abby Lee Dance Company.


00:07:02.722 --> 00:07:04.791 line:95%,end
All right, girls, love to talk to you
a little bit about this number.

00:07:04.857 --> 00:07:08.528 line:95%,end
