00:07:14.734 --> 00:07:16.202 line:95%,end
to do her own choreography.

00:07:16.269 --> 00:07:18.471 line:95%,end
You come out, you're a free spirit.

00:07:18.538 --> 00:07:19.972 line:95%,end
You have all the privileges.

00:07:20.039 --> 00:07:21.574 line:95%,end
You're allowed to do anything.

00:07:21.641 --> 00:07:24.877 line:95%,end
I've chosen Maddie
to be the lead role in this piece

00:07:24.944 --> 00:07:27.680 line:95%,end
because she is perfect for the part.

00:07:27.747 --> 00:07:31.451 line:95%,end
She has the facial expressions
that can tell the judges the story.

00:07:31.517 --> 00:07:35.288 line:95%,end
You guys don't have any of those
pleasures of life that she has.

00:07:35.354 --> 00:07:39.459 line:95%,end
She's different. You're going to make her
want to be like you.

00:07:39.525 --> 00:07:41.928 line:95%,end
CHRISTI: I'm pretty sure
when she was discussing the group dance,

00:07:41.994 --> 00:07:43.663 line:95%,end
there's one little girl is special

00:07:43.729 --> 00:07:44.997 line:95%,end
and they all want to make her conform--

00:07:45.064 --> 00:07:46.833 line:95%,end
like, who do you think that's going to be?

00:07:46.899 --> 00:07:50.269 line:95%,end
