on Nia being different,

00:08:17.830 --> 00:08:19.765 line:95%,end
since that's a featured part of the dance.

00:08:19.832 --> 00:08:22.401 line:95%,end
The storyline is,
is that Maddie is above us

00:08:22.468 --> 00:08:25.872 line:95%,end
and we're trying to bring
her back to be like us.

00:08:25.938 --> 00:08:27.673 line:95%,end
MELISSA: <i>Kelly and Christi</i>
<i>are reading way too much</i>

00:08:27.740 --> 00:08:28.641 line:95%,end
<i>into this group dance.</i>

00:08:28.708 --> 00:08:30.743 line:5%,start
It's like they are always
looking for something

00:08:30.810 --> 00:08:32.311 line:5%,start
