00:08:36.782 --> 00:08:39.051 line:95%,end
-it turns into this big thing.
-Everybody celebrates everybody.

00:08:39.118 --> 00:08:41.954 line:95%,end
Oh, okay.
That's why you talk about my daughter.

00:08:42.021 --> 00:08:43.389 line:95%,end
