00:08:43.456 --> 00:08:45.258 line:95%,end
MELISSA: Christi is taking
Chloe out of school,

00:08:45.324 --> 00:08:46.425 line:95%,end
and then she's taking her to the movies.

00:08:48.394 --> 00:08:50.696 line:95%,end
