00:08:50.763 --> 00:08:53.266 line:95%,end
-You talk about my daughter all the time.
-CHRISTI: No, I (bleep).

00:08:53.332 --> 00:08:56.068 line:95%,end
I talk about the way Abby favors her!

00:08:56.135 --> 00:08:58.437 line:95%,end
Have any of these women up here
heard me talk about Maddie

00:08:58.504 --> 00:09:00.039 line:95%,end
