00:39:55.526 --> 00:39:57.228 line:95%,end
Cathy, you got to man these boys up.

00:39:57.294 --> 00:39:58.763 line:95%,end
-Come on.
-Oh, please.

00:39:58.829 --> 00:39:59.930 line:95%,end
MITCHELL: Tell her we're pretty manly.

00:39:59.997 --> 00:40:01.132 line:95%,end
CATHY:
Tell us what's masculine.

00:40:01.198 --> 00:40:02.199 line:95%,end
Yeah, really.

00:40:02.266 --> 00:40:03.567 line:95%,end
I didn't have any boys
in a number today.

00:40:03.634 --> 00:40:06.237 line:95%,end
No, but Abby, even your girls don't.

00:40:06.303 --> 00:40:07.338 line:95%,end
Don't do what?

00:40:07.405 --> 00:40:08.472 line:95%,end
-MITCHELL: They don't do that difficulty.
-CATHY: Your girls--

00:40:08.539 --> 00:40:09.740 line:95%,end
-Your girls don't do...
-MITCHELL: They don't do that difficulty.

00:40:09.807 --> 00:40:11.142 line:95%,end
...what's fresh and new.

00:40:11.208 --> 00:40:12.610 line:95%,end
Fresh and new?

00:40:12.676 --> 00:40:14.845 line:95%,end
Straight legs and stretched feet
will never go out of style.

00:40:14.912 --> 00:40:16.213 line:95%,end
CATHY:
Oh, you're right. They won't.

00:40:16.280 --> 00:40:17.181 line:95%,end
You're absolutely right.

00:40:17.248 --> 00:40:19.617 line:95%,end
So then you better get on some
of them who have sickled feet.

00:40:19.683 --> 00:40:21.519 line:95%,end
-ABBY: Let's--come on, Cathy...
-CATHY: And you better get on some--

00:40:21.585 --> 00:40:24.255 line:95%,end
let's put Vivi-Anne right
up against Mackenzie.

00:40:24.321 --> 00:40:26.524 line:95%,end
Let's put the two 8-year-olds
up against each other.

00:40:26.590 --> 00:40:27.691 line:95%,end
CATHY: You know what?
I have to hold back.

00:40:27.758 --> 00:40:31.962 line:95%,end
Because my little 8-year-old has improved
week after week after week.

00:40:32.029 --> 00:40:33.364 line:95%,end
Because they don't go to school.

00:40:33.431 --> 00:40:35.032 line:5%,start
-My little Vivi-Anne--
-Excuse me?

00:40:35.099 --> 00:40:36.400 line:5%,start
-My daughter goes to school!
-My little Vivi-Anne

00:40:36.467 --> 00:40:37.768 line:5%,start
reads third grade books.

00:40:37.835 --> 00:40:39.470 line:5%,start
-Shut up!
-Don't tell me to shut up.

00:40:39.537 --> 00:40:43.307 line:5%,start
My daughter is smart
and she goes to school every day!

00:40:43.374 --> 00:40:44.208 line:5%,start
-Hey, listen!
-MELISSA: My daughter--

00:40:44.275 --> 00:40:46.911 line:5%,start
It was you who called Vivi a human prop!

00:40:46.977 --> 00:40:48.279 line:5%,start
-MELISSA: She is!
-So don't tell me to shut up!

00:40:48.345 --> 00:40:49.647 line:5%,start
-MELISSA: Yes, but I know--
-I think you need to take

00:40:49.713 --> 00:40:51.916 line:5%,start
your little technicolor ass
and get out of here.

